    "### Advantages: Accurate\n",
    "### Disadvantages: Slow\n",
    "\n",
    "### Working of MICE Algorithm:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Actual Dataset\n",
    "2. Removing the target column\n",
    "3. Introduced some fake nan values\n",
    "\n",
    "### Steps\n",
    "   \n",
    "1. Fill all the NaN values with mean of respective cols.\n",
    "2. Remove all col1 missing values\n",
    "3. Predict the missing values of col1 using other cols\n",
    "4. Remove all col2 missing values\n",
    "5. Predict the missing values of col2 using cols.\n",
    "6. Remove all col3 values."
   ]
